5:
Looking into what's causing the tremors, 
huh? That's quite a tall order.
8:
I understand... 
but the higher-ups think you all have 
what it takes.
11:
That's one way to convince me. 
What say you, men?!
14:
Challenge accepted! 
There ain't nothing we can't do with you 
by our side, Leon!
18:
Hah! That's what I like to hear! 
Now get your asses in gear, 'cause we're 
leaving now!
23:
Hey, Leon! 
We still on for training tomorrow?
27:
Sorry, Alk. 
It looks like I'll have to bow out for a 
while.
30:
Looks like I'll be investigating what's 
causing these tremors... 
I can't promise when I'll be back.
35: Alk. I won't ask you to join me.
38:
And it's not because you're weak, 
but there's still much you need to learn.
40:
If I were to bite the dust, you'd be left 
on your own, right?
44: I'm still worried about you though.
47:
I appreciate that. 
But we can't afford to lose someone 
young in this biz, you know?
51:
Treat me to something nice to eat when 
I get back, okay?
58:
Say, Stella... 
If I were to die in battle somehow, 
what would you do?
61:
I wouldn't let something like that 
happen.
65:
Heh... I thought you might say 
something like that.
68:
You were planning on going anyway, 
weren't you? Let's get a move on.
78:
A damn shame, honestly... 
I was hopin' we'd get to spend some 
more time together.
81:
They say it's bad luck to talk about yer 
lover here in the Kaleidoscope, Leon.
84:
I ain't talking about a woman, dummy... 
I've taken on a student.
86:
A rookie of yer own, eh? 
Must be nice, showin' someone else the 
ropes.
88:
It's not bad. 
I've got high hopes for the kid... 
He might be the one to carry on my 
legacy, you know?
91:
You'd better have some stories ready 
for him then, eh?
95:
Yeah. Now, enough chit-chat. 
We've got another level up ahead, so
110: Don't let them near the midways!
114:
I wonder what they'd say if they saw me 
like this...
124:
There's no use in thinking about the ifs 
or maybes... 
All I need to do is focus on how I can 
help you... right here, right now!
127:
We won't allow you to perish here. 
And I'm sure the others feel the same 
way.
130:
You heard the lady, Leon... 
Looks like we're still kids at heart.
133:
Heh... You idiots. 
You damned, beautiful idiots!
138:
We're ADVENTURERS! 
Reason be damned, we'll overcome the 
impossible and grab our dreams with 
our own bare hands!
140:
We'll make it outta here alive, 
even if it kills us! 
Let's show this Kaleidoscope what 
we're made of!
146:
Geez... You're one hell of a daredevil, 
you know that, rookie? 
Light's gonna kill us for that stunt.
149:
But let me apologize, Alk. 
I... shouldn't have underestimated you.
151:
You've indeed got a lot to learn, 
but you're an adventurer through 
and throughI'll try not to forget that 
next time.
155:
Thanks, Leon! 
Our lessons are still on though, right?
159:
You bet. And let me tell you now, it ain't 
gonna be easy! 
A full-fledged adventurer's gotta be 
ready for anything!
165:
Hah, don't look so gloom already! 
Surviving another day more than 
enough reason to celebrate!
